Inspired by : http://wiki.apache.org/cassandra/Locking
Baker's Algorithm: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lamport%27s_bakery_algorithm



Performance Test: June 24, 2011
3-Node Cassandra cluster: (Rackspace/8GB nodes)
3-Load test nodes: 1 Lock creation/2 Lock acquisition (Rackspace/2GB Nodes)


Single Node throughput: 81858 Locks/600sec, 81322 Locks/600sec
Aggregate throughput: 271 locks acquired/sec